        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-17",
        "text": "And He walks with me, and He talks with me,",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 18
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -300,
          "y_px": 285
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#000000",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-18",
        "text": "And He tells me I am His own,",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 18
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -324,
          "y_px": 311
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#000000",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-19",
        "text": "And the joy we share as we tarry there,",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 18
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -306,
          "y_px": 334
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#000000",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-20",
        "text": "None other has ever known.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 18
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -312,
          "y_px": 361
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#000000",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-21",
        "text": "I&apos;d stay in the garden with Him",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 18
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 180,
          "y_px": 282
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#000000",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-22",
        "text": "Tho&apos; the night around me be falling;",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 18
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 183,
          "y_px": 303
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#000000",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-23",
        "text": "But He bids me go; thro&apos; the voice of woe,",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 18
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 198,
          "y_px": 333
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#000000",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-24",
